      "date": "2023-03-23 20:58:08.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nPicking up from my comments on https://review.whamcloud.com/c/ex/lustre-release/+/50346\n\nThis fixes a key use of cl_page_delete without checking if the page is in use.  We have other unchecked uses of cl_page_delete, but fixing this one is sufficient to allow the tests to pass without the fix from Panda.  (I will get to the others.)\n\nI've pushed two test patches which disable the seqlock/retry fix to demonstrate and double-check this, one based on this patch:\nhttps://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/50393\nAnd one on master (which should fail):\nhttps://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/50394",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
